the Vegetables:\n1 cup Surti Papdi (Val Papdi), stringed and shelled or split\n8 small Baby Potatoes, peeled and slit (do not cut through)\n4 small Indian Eggplants (Baingan), slit lengthwise (do not cut through)\n1 cup Purple Yam (Kand), peeled and cubed large\n1 cup Sweet Potato (Shakarkand), peeled and cubed large\n1 large Raw Banana (Kacha Kela), peeled and sliced thick\n\nFor the Methi Muthia